<span data-type="media" id="fs-id1170572168980" data-alt="Photo of an iceboat in action.">
<img src="/resources/a810a0fa86f425ececa30f300f68e666c2e04cc3/CNX_Calc_Figure_05_00_001.jpg" data-media-type="image/jpeg" alt="Photo of an iceboat in action."/>
